{"tid":2153127,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"大不了飛鴿傳書嘛！- 李純恩","createTime":"2020-08-12T10:57:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-12T11:16:03.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"71784a6ae8619d75887db1a19df1fbc7ebf17bf5","tid":2153127,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T10:57:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20200812/2562UMCFENAC3EOTNZCL6RU3BQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20200812%2F2562UMCFENAC3EOTNZCL6RU3BQ%2F&d=bHO956KQIgsLkYPN5Vvl7bKDDpXBBweeKWShnQU3kRY%3D&h=127bdc88\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20200812%2F2562UMCFENAC3EOTNZCL6RU3BQ%2F&h=80a5f3c9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20200812/2562UMCFENAC3EOTNZCL6RU3BQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n大不了飛鴿傳書嘛！- 李純恩<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/6SqGu6U4wEN2-srb8jAekW1x4-E=/2048x1359/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/YCCXZHCBVBCQNIAMZCL4XNEHVM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F6SqGu6U4wEN2-srb8jAekW1x4-E%3D%2F2048x1359%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FYCCXZHCBVBCQNIAMZCL4XNEHVM.jpg&h=236ae379&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n生活在美國的北京人說，。。。。。。。。。停了微信用什麼跟中國熟人聯繫呢？<br />\n<br />\n我說社交網絡又不是只有微信，不用微信，Facebook、IG、WhatsApp，還有你們喜歡看那個郭文貴胡說八道的「推特」都可以嘛。<br />\n<br />\n北京人說，這些我在美國都可以用，但中國沒有一種用得上，老早封鎖了。要用就要翻牆，麻煩得要命，還不一定翻得出去。現在的情況是我沒微信用，他們只能用微信，那不是失聯了嗎？<br />\n<br />\n我說算了，俄羅斯兩年前就不給用微信了，又沒見中國人吵，難道中國人只受俄羅斯人欺侮？。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"c3a80364bb70f0bf6d2cd2b3a043a37622bfb664","tid":2153127,"uid":286017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T11:01:41.000Z","msg":"個個把口愛國反美但成班撚樣一有機會就轉資產做美金，移民去美國做自由人嘛，邊有柒頭走得出中國又鐘個頭入俄羅斯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"555a112fe88241209680302c62a6f23bbae27c85","tid":2153127,"uid":87511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T11:12:08.000Z","msg":"抽水功力都唔差，有才子六七成"},{"pid":"6f5c949891334c31da681e0e08aa63764836cf47","tid":2153127,"uid":39277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T11:16:03.000Z","msg":"佢之前有係頭條寫專欄<br />\n<br />\n好似好多大陸朋友<br />\n<br />\n一直搞唔清佢立場"}]}